<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yī shēng hái shì yào chuán fú yīn 迦南311</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wèi le fú yīn de xìng wàng, wǒ men gān yuàn shě jǐ.
 tīng bù dào mǔ qīn huáng hūn huàn nǐ guī.
 wèi le fú yīn de xìng wàng, wǒ men yuàn yì gēn suí.
 bù guǎn fēng yǔ lái zì nǎ lǐ. wǒ men shì yī jiā rén,
 yǒu yī kē bù biàn de xīn, tóng mìng yùn gòng shēng cún.
 wǒ men jīn tiān dòng shēn, wǒ men xiàn zài dòng shēn,
 yī shēng hái shì yào chuán fú yīn.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>311</hymn_number>
</song>